{%- comment -%}
  SNIPPET: Offer Drawer - line-no-375
  DESCRIPTION:
    - A product-level modal component that displays available offers for the current product.
    - Uses Shopify's built-in modal system (`modal-opener` and `modal-dialog`) for accessibility and native drawer behavior.
    - Triggered via the “See All” button in the product-offers section.

  LOGIC OVERVIEW:
    1. The snippet is rendered inside `main-product.liquid` within the `.offers-product` wrapper.
    2. The `<modal-opener>` triggers the `<modal-dialog>` when the “See All” button is clicked.
    3. The `<modal-dialog>` displays a structured list of promotional offers with image, title, description, meta, and CTA links.
    4. The modal can be closed via the close icon (`icon-close`).

  DEPENDENCIES:
    - CSS:
        • component-offer.css  → controls layout, spacing, and responsive design for offer modal and items
        • Quick-add.css  → style for offer drawer - line no - 84 - 89
    - JS:
        • Uses Shopify's built-in modal system (no custom JS required)
    - Snippets:
        • icon-offer
        • custom-arrow-right
        • offer-meta
        • offer-arrow
        • icon-close
    - Used in:
        • main-product.liquid (within `.offers-product` container)

  NOTES:
    - Designed with semantic markup using <modal-opener> and <modal-dialog> for accessibility.
    - Styling does not override global typography or colors — inherits theme variables.
{%- endcomment -%}


